snippet.textDisplay: To whoever is reading this I am crying uncontrollably it has been a dream to see sindhi culture come to the forefront we lost our home Sindh but let's not loose us our culture our language and music and dance. Brothers n sisters you have no idea how many sindhis are waiting for this. And surprisingly this story you are talking about is my story of resilience and come back. Ho chokri jeka kehinji na budhe, pahinji halaye, sajiyun ladayun ladi kare wapas aayi aahe woh ma ahinyan, jehinje laye sajhi kudrat tariyun vajaindi woh ma ahinyan. This is my comeback song. ❤ dadho pyar
